{"tid":2499281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得講白話嘅先係高人一等？？","createTime":"2021-04-21T18:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T20:39:53.000Z","uid":139319,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb51b9c5a4e2710e627e8bb173c2a4f23e38885","tid":2499281,"uid":139319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"係我心目中，鬼國支那狗/日本狗/黑鬼/白皮豬全撚部都係一樣咁仆街，當然支狗最賤。<br />\n我覺得只有嶺南文化下嘅大粵圈講白話嘅人先係上等人。<br />\n我承認我係一個種族主義者。"},{"pid":"abc967303b9ebe07380e0717d86da4371c6380a5","tid":2499281,"uid":24281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T18:35:07.000Z","msg":"岩（點頭？"},{"pid":"29193bd2cf3a3b6d492ef74bdd31b7606116d32f","tid":2499281,"uid":139319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T18:39:55.000Z","msg":"補充：<br />\n類似我哋而家嘅白話係公元前100年已形成，比支式北佬話早過千年"},{"pid":"7a6b58ddb0b490c05fc03a829658cf0b9c3f39a2","tid":2499281,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T20:39:53.000Z","msg":"講白話嘅上等人對個世界嘅貢獻大唔大？"}]}